{"tid":1390772,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"美聯工商舖 | 獨家代理 | 觀塘瑞和街地舖 售價1.2億","createTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T09:18:11.000Z","uid":7439,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bec7fa13f225e0ec3c1a21e42aa8cc5251e9505a","tid":1390772,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T08:31:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S-fdGSxCTVI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS-fdGSxCTVI&d=0Ti31m2ePiHoIE7ADo8qnSHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=48b40377\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S-fdGSxCTVI</a><br />\n位置卓越、人流極旺的民生靚舖，它鄰近觀塘百億重建發展區核心，而且一個物業，坐享兩個租客、三個門面，吸盡區內海量人流，加上未來區內發展前景非常理想，是投資的優質選擇！#工商舖#觀塘#舖位<br />\n<br />\n物業編號：S038801<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美聯旺舖表示，觀塘瑞和街28至48號南安大樓地下A(48)號舖，面積約1800方呎，連閣樓，意向售價約1.2億元，呎價約6.66萬元，將連約出售。<br />\n<br />\n物業單位為三面單邊大舖，擁有特大門面，間隔四正實用，買家用途更彈性，可分隔作出租之用。<br />\n<br />\n上述物業是觀塘區的富貴街市舖位，地理位置極佳，正正在裕民坊發展區核心，以及瑞和街雙門面的中央位置，街市供應區內大部分市民的日常需要，人流暢旺。"},{"pid":"5bae14a5f585b81cfb21ba18d5372d981e9bd99d","tid":1390772,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T14:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec3db881908f1e8a2bf06d67dad9b63e386a4c6","tid":1390772,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"呢度你都想撈客？"},{"pid":"960cf60c290fa51c0ee0a1a8e7a7e707d167a74d","tid":1390772,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2ec3db881908f1e8a2bf06d67dad9b63e386a4c6","tid":1390772,"uid":86592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"呢度你都想撈客？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T09:18:11.000Z","msg":"幫世清問"}]}